kart.name: KART
kart.desc: Dragon Kart is the first 3D Play-to-Earn Battle Racing game built on Binance Smart Chain, the characters in the game are taken from a Pikalong comics series by a Vietnamese well-known artist Thang Fly*. This series has been exposed to millions of Vietnamese users in Zalo, the most used communication app in Vietnam (can be compared to Wechat in China or Kakao in Korea) for roughly 5 years.  *Thang Fly is a Vietnamese artist influencer with 1.4M+ followers on Facebook.  Highlights: Talented team with 7-10 years of experiences in technology and related fields. The MVP is available Demo product is ready to be tested.
